snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin': Yellow (Trailer)
snippet.description:
we look forward to seeing you very soon.
https://gamebanana.com/wips/82895

we present to you a love letter to UNDERTALE YELLOW in the style of an FNF mod.
and, of course, it is suitably named: Friday Night Funkin': Yellow (woahh)
ASSETS IN THIS TRAILER ARE SUBJECT TO CHANGE!!
(every gameplay clip was recorded in an early, unfinished build!)

V1 only includes 3 UNDERTALE YELLOW bosses, but more are currently in the works, so don't worry if your favorite character isnt in this trailer, chances are its only a matter of time until we get to them.

check out our community server.
https://discord.gg/cSQYTCR7aA
& our twitter.
https://twitter.com/FNFYELLOW

FNFY CREDITS: 
Trailer creation: Nexa Verglas & ByzaFyre
Trailer music: Fellow Gamer
Gaster animations: Ultraweh
Clover sprites: Slimykris
Dalv sprites: Eyeben
Martlet sprites: Bugsm4x
Yellow Sans & Frisk sprites: Zane0744
Chara sprites: Zane0744 & SlimyKris
Wing Gaster sprites: Ultraweh

links to socials & everyone else can be found on our gamebanana!
more detailed credits will be in-game too.


UNDERTALE YELLOW CREDITS:
MasterSwordRemix & the UNDERTALE YELLOW team. 
https://gamejolt.com/games/UndertaleYellow/136925

MORE CREDITS?!?!:
UNDERTALE: Toby Fox
https://undertale.com/
Wing Gaster & UT Battle Mode creator: yosheDev
https://gamejolt.com/games/undertale-battle-mode/115477
